{"tid":90543,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，好多香港人比大陸人更乞人憎","createTime":"2017-01-22T07:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T17:38:32.000Z","uid":58089,"like":449,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02dbd2298b342528bed74a3194e3aca753354f90","tid":90543,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"香港有好多人都狗眼看人低、多多要求、成撚日以為世界圍住佢轉、欺善怕惡<br />\n<br />\n讀u做過幾份服務業pt，用一個字形容，大陸人係煩，香港人係賤<br />\n<br />\n做錯野，大陸人會嘈幾句，通常扮死狗道歉就無野；得罪香港人，佢唔食唔訓都要玩撚死你，試過有客投訴完過幾日打黎問個同事比人炒左未 (個同事只係記錯個價錢)<br />\n<br />\n好多香港客扮識人，r著數，唔比折佢佢又投訴你態度差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比幾百蚊以為自己係大爺，又唔係有錢"},{"pid":"907099c355a4f630794890233f3ad4821a6fc814","tid":90543,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"預左比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做pt果時成班同事都寧願serve 大陸人，起碼屌客都唔會有後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸人你屌完佢佢都笑笑口咁唔知做乜"},{"pid":"5aec163e6fd04ddbfc37d1c22143b959d809169c","tid":90543,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ca6d5977b26d3699d1360a1bae39b05e169de0","tid":90543,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f2a22c3cc7a621d44a165f3c828ccc9f15da5da","tid":90543,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6f153b0e729a2f285de9db704aeb59f13d066da","tid":90543,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"6af9811b8aee9127b7762ce72d302235c4827304","tid":90543,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班sales態度咪又無咁撚差，講到自己好撚委屈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打，睇下你去邊間啦<br />\n我自己做過果d，長期四萬咁口，又要唔好意思前唔好意思後<br />\n做過銀行，講漏句&quot;麻煩哂&quot; 都會比公司扣分<br />\n<br />\n有好多香港人欺善怕惡，你又唔見有人投訴澳牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28555941a89e7371b30111ee56c4205c18fdad8c","tid":90543,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:02:11.000Z","msg":"因為大多數大陸人都係過幾日就走<br />\n無時間懶得追究<br />\n有錢有時間果堆都唔會玩埋咁無聊既野<br />\n而且果度唔係佢地主場通常會收斂小小<br />\n而香港人反正長期係度<br />\n想玩你只需要得閒打個電話都煩死你<br />\n而且係主場識得點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最恨d大集團sales成隻跟尾狗咁<br />\n叫左我自己睇佢都照跟<br />\n到底係邊個無腦既仆街定埋d咁既規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cbb5d4892a474ac06e3a2ca31d0289e974e4da","tid":90543,"uid":53233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"返緊服務業嘅我表示認同<br />\n啲香港客會為左小小野就係到發哂爛渣<br />\n甚至有啲會格硬搵野投訴r著數<br />\n真係cheap到冇人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1930856950a55131ba2c3cd2cb96ba8af89de1","tid":90543,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"香港班廢老廢中  真係西撚到無人有 <br />\n<br />\n做過服務業實見識過"},{"pid":"a0c014149e19cfad76c830e64c4da6bfa8236502","tid":90543,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班sales態度咪又無咁撚差，講到自己好撚委屈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打，睇下你去邊間啦<br />\n我自己做過果d，長期四萬咁口，又要唔好意思前唔好意思後<br />\n做過銀行，講漏句&quot;麻煩哂&quot; 都會比公司扣分<br />\n<br />\n有好多香港人欺善怕惡，你又唔見有人投訴澳牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係欺善怕惡<br />\n係投黎有無用<br />\n大集團背後成個system可以玩<br />\n背後有一大堆惡過你既人<br />\n又有大堆根本無可能跟得哂既rules<br />\n細鋪仔可能個sales對上就老闆<br />\n連個老闆都會撐個sales<br />\n投黎都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70067d7cc9f3b48e57f2c7974cd2ca431eff46a1","tid":90543,"uid":16730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"Agger 由其是果班死中產 以為自己好撚有錢"},{"pid":"885fedf7d60b58df37d30c65248083fd594286eb","tid":90543,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2071573e7c9597b76f952452d0c6f997dc9b69","tid":90543,"uid":58089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agger 由其是果班死中產 以為自己好撚有錢</blockquote><br />\n窮既多數粗人把口難聽d，但直腸直肚，唔會做埋小動作<br />\n有錢既我自己私底下都識幾個，真係隨時唔洗供拎錢買棟別墅果d，真係好有禮貌 (二世祖唔計)<br />\n反而中產以為自己好有錢，狗眼看人低，通常仆街既離唔開公務員、老師、港媽，呢d你得罪佢佢一定投訴到你比人炒為止"},{"pid":"5ec7b833124b2543983a6164f30f9e36326a7165","tid":90543,"uid":46577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"冇錯樓主都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5b327b4e457c8d7a1260ddb201bfe8f5ee4381","tid":90543,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇錯樓主都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你當我係啦"},{"pid":"b92cdc7446d132701a2083a9e7938a2f50721a47","tid":90543,"uid":56023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貪小便宜, 畀少少錢就當自己係大爺西口西面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2060a83d72dd9d86ac50f3dfd7a25942a90213","tid":90543,"uid":56023,"like"