ckquote>Agger 由其是果班死中產 以為自己好撚有錢</blockquote><br />\n窮既多數粗人把口難聽d，但直腸直肚，唔會做埋小動作<br />\n有錢既我自己私底下都識幾個，真係隨時唔洗供拎錢買棟別墅果d，真係好有禮貌 (二世祖唔計)<br />\n反而中產以為自己好有錢，狗眼看人低，通常仆街既離唔開公務員、老師、港媽，呢d你得罪佢佢一定投訴到你比人炒為止</blockquote><br />\n屌 啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太古城果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99abe8080634f126bb68270af805fea442627e2","tid":90543,"uid":19295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:48:55.000Z","msg":"做緊炒散 啲客最鍾意問邊張信用卡有折"},{"pid":"f200c2316fda4f8421ad4696c34af852493e5873","tid":90543,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:20:37.000Z","msg":"認同，仲要咁多正評<br />\n<br />\n呢個post令我見識到連登同高登不同之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ae960ab8a5e66c687addfd25745447aa729961","tid":90543,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做緊炒散 啲客最鍾意問邊張信用卡有折</blockquote><br />\n呢樣有咩問題 態度正常咪得"},{"pid":"a77c5352f7d77e2b309f2241113523a06fabd2a9","tid":90543,"uid":60082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為大多數大陸人都係過幾日就走<br />\n無時間懶得追究<br />\n有錢有時間果堆都唔會玩埋咁無聊既野<br />\n而且果度唔係佢地主場通常會收斂小小<br />\n而香港人反正長期係度<br />\n想玩你只需要得閒打個電話都煩死你<br />\n而且係主場識得點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最恨d大集團sales成隻跟尾狗咁<br />\n叫左我自己睇佢都照跟<br />\n到底係邊個無腦既仆街定埋d咁既規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常私佣先會死跟 驚你買野俾其他sales搶"},{"pid":"baa8a82e6977c49bb7cb5088e5ff5e9bf49e3903","tid":90543,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re